other_tests.findings: Infiltrating ductal carcinoma, grade 2 of 3, involving most of all five cores.

other_tests.procedure_name: Right partial mastectomy and sentinel lymph node biopsy
other_tests.findings: Invasive ductal carcinoma measuring 0.9 cm by 0.8 cm by 0.5 cm, classified as grade 2 of 3, with invasion of lymphatic vessels but not blood vessels. Several nests of metastatic ductal carcinoma in the sentinel lymph node, less than 0.02 cm in diameter, without extracapsular extension.
Detected positive tumor cells on three slides from deeper levels of the tissue block.
